AWS availablity zones(in AWS reagion - min: 3, max: 6)
AWS Data Centers (in AZ)
AWS Edge Locations/Points of Presence (globally 400+)


How to choose an AWS Region?
    Near to customers
    Pricing (pricing varies region to region)
    Region where required service is available
    Compliance with data governance and legal requirements







